{"tid":713782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【七一遊行】盧偉聰：再呼籲市民勿在東角道聚集及出發","createTime":"2018-06-23T06:21:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T13:40:11.000Z","uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e93a73323b4d3cb255d8e6696a1eaf15ebf6d9f5","tid":713782,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T06:21:57.000Z","msg":"由於維園球場再次被建制組織優先租用，舉辦七一遊行的民間人權陣線今年本計劃在銅鑼灣東道出發，但遭警方反對，發出的不反對通知書要求以維園草坪起步，民陣已提出上訴。警務處處長盧偉聰今天表示，警方已被上訴委員會通知主辦單位提出上訴，警方屆時會據理力爭。<br />\n<br />\n他稱要再次強調，警方絕對尊重市民遊行示威及表達言論自由，只是希望能保護他們及公共安全。「維園我們沿用多年，證明是安全與比較適合大型活動起點的地方，我再次呼籲主辦單位不要呼籲市民在東角道聚集及出發，因為只會影響其他市民在維園聚集，及出發時大家互相爭路造成混亂場面，絕對沒有其他意思。」<br />\n<br />\n盧偉聰日前曾公開表示，如遊行不按不反對通知書要求在維園草坪出發，在東角道聚集的人群可能觸犯非法集結罪。"},{"pid":"56216d6ee0fbf8c67ed5fd41ea13b9f799f34fe2","tid":713782,"uid":104431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T06:29:55.000Z","msg":"行街都犯法?"},{"pid":"3939ddd389b1f015989d68d8a489569176b16b2a","tid":713782,"uid":176366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T06:52:43.000Z","msg":"大家夠鐘去鳩嗚喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed09233def6c4ea354d3bce028189d0ca2b47ed","tid":713782,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T06:58:05.000Z","msg":"到時去東角道 shopping <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6b993eb0f361f2a70b48b04e580ed0cf160ba83","tid":713782,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T06:59:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/9/9e/Trying_to_scare_me.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/400?cb=20070109090620\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F9%2F9e%2FTrying_to_scare_me.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%2Fscale-to-width-down%2F400%3Fcb%3D20070109090620&h=5c01f215&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd01d341497bd94f82b5c71576feadfc5a061d03","tid":713782,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T07:03:35.000Z","msg":"Sogo 同 金百利商場 好多野睇,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   值得去."},{"pid":"544f5f3ac6611bfa10309e37344c8da6c2d8392d","tid":713782,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T07:57:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c70bcf7f4d33f9c37bfb1df6ef8a182196b15c11","tid":713782,"uid":171786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T08:12:56.000Z","msg":"其實邊度出發有乜分別，做乜一走要東角道出發"},{"pid":"8ac3ad74c37adbb4408599ac31b33026fb60350d","tid":713782,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T08:18:45.000Z","msg":"盧偉聰我屌你老母呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea6f19932c7379b3c2463c7f6ae474c7ae539ee","tid":713782,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T13:40:11.000Z","msg":"姓盧的請學好貴國語言：<br />\n<br />\n第三十五條 中華人民共和國公民有言論、出版、集會、結社、游(遊)行、示威的自由。"}]}